OL,3,CEnd the scandal: MP calls for rugby
OL,4,Cleague legend to be made a Sir
OL,6,FMPs have heard calls for a knighthood
OL,7,Ffor rugby league hero Billy Boston to
OL,8,Fend the "scandal" that no player from
OL,9,Fthe sport has ever been knighted.
OL,11,FBoston scored 478 tries in 487 matches
OL,12,Ffor Wigan after making the rugby
OL,13,Fswitch from union to league in 1953.
OL,15,FThe 90-year-old revealed in 2016 he
OL,16,Fhad been living with vascular
OL,17,Fdementia. He has been appointed an
OL,18,FMBE, the third-highest ranking award
OL,19,Fwithin the Order of the British
OL,20,FEmpire, after CBE and OBE but before a
OL,21,Fknighthood or damehood.
