OL,3,CEnd the scandal: MP calls for rugby
OL,4,Cleague legend to be made a Sir
OL,6,FCommons Speaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle has
OL,7,Fcampaigned on the issue and previously
OL,8,Fsaid it is a "major injustice" that no
OL,9,Frugby league player has ever been
OL,10,Fknighted.
OL,12,FDuring business questions, Labour MP
OL,13,Ffor Makerfield Josh Simons said: "Mr
OL,14,FSpeaker, rugby league fans like
OL,15,Fyourself and others in this chamber
OL,16,Fwill know and love my most famous
OL,17,Fconstituent, Billy Boston.
