OL,3,CEnd the scandal: MP calls for rugby
OL,4,Cleague legend to be made a Sir
OL,6,F"Before I came into this chamber, I
OL,7,Fwas informed that Billy is not well,
OL,8,Fand local councillors in my
OL,9,Fconstituency have started a petition
OL,10,Fto ensure that he receives a
OL,11,Fknighthood while that's still possible.
OL,13,F"It is a scandal that for over a
OL,14,Fcentury, no rugby football league hero
OL,15,Fhas received a knighthood, a scandal
OL,16,Fthat we must recognise."
OL,18,FSir Lindsay wished Boston well,
OL,19,Fadding: "Nobody has ever scored tries
OL,20,Flike Billy Boston."
